	select SND_SOC_SOF_INTEL_ATOM_HIFI_EP
	help
	  This adds support for Sound Open Firmware for Intel(R) platforms
	  using the Tangier/Merrifield processors.
	  Say Y if you have such a device.
	  If unsure select "N".

